                            <html:h1 class="title">Qt Designer Integration</html:h1>
                            <html:span class="subtitle"></html:span>
                            <!-- $$$stylesheet-designer.html-description -->
                            <html:div class="descr">
                                <html:a name="details"></html:a>
                                <html:p>Qt Designer{Qt Designer} is an excellent tool to preview
                                    style sheets. You can right-click on any widget in Designer and
                                    select <html:b>Change <html:a href="stylesheet.html#stylesheet"
                                            >styleSheet</html:a>...</html:b> to set the style
                                    sheet.</html:p>
                                <html:p class="centerAlign"><html:img alt=""
                                        src="images/designer-stylesheet-options.png"
                                     /></html:p><html:p>In Qt 4.2 and later, Qt Designer also
                                    includes a style sheet syntax highlighter and validator. The
                                    validator indicates if the syntax is valid or invalid, at the
                                    bottom left of the <html:b>Edit Style Sheet</html:b>
                                    dialog.</html:p>
                                <html:p class="centerAlign"><html:img alt=""
                                        src="images/designer-validator-highlighter.png"
                                     /></html:p><html:p>When you click <html:b>OK</html:b> or
                                        <html:b>Apply</html:b>, Qt Designer will automatically
                                    display the widget with its new stylesheet.</html:p>
                                <html:p class="centerAlign"><html:img alt=""
                                        src="images/designer-stylesheet-usage.png"
                                 /></html:p></html:div>
